{"tid":2007291,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"午餐 蝦扁意粉","createTime":"2020-05-08T09:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T02:40:17.000Z","uid":62277,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f13469ecdbce9924b41b1704f62594accb52e983","tid":2007291,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"主要做街坊生意既餐廳仔<br />\n<br />\n喺午餐牌上揀咗個最清既嚟食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oynuudq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foynuudq.jpg&h=8d95b7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好簡單既一碟意粉<br />\n煮得尚算有咬口<br />\n茄醬清新，鹹酸平衡得好<br />\n隻味有啲似肉醬意粉<br />\n如果再少返啲汁就更加好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ksN0no.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ksN0no.jpg&h=4940bbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅宋湯唔係hea整<br />\n落咗唔少牛肉<br />\n夠濃夠辣之餘又有肉味"},{"pid":"13a93b71a8f41ab9288386c0d8bc6b78a3e106da","tid":2007291,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"【郭偉强找數】<br />\n<br />\n呼籲集體投訴社工之恥郭偉强蓄意襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉强社工註冊編號：11071<br />\n罪行：普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n下載「社會工作者註冊局」投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2FDocuments%2Fcomplaint.pdf&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=e8247b38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"8100d3ece4080b33d2b1692e9441628728c51469","tid":2007291,"uid":316702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr